{"tid":2358842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"保錡單野證明左藝人有第三者根本唔洗公開交代 以往咁多單嘅藝人都柒左啦","createTime":"2021-01-08T12:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T09:02:26.000Z","uid":368777,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"71d2ef3564c1eb3a8748fb232ea5596ca7f0e0a8","tid":2358842,"uid":368777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><ins>回帶</ins></strong></span></p><br />\n<br />\n2017：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20170407/F42XWNF6AAMEGLG4WLEM6ULCTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20170407%2FF42XWNF6AAMEGLG4WLEM6ULCTQ%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=9137812d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20170407%2FF42XWNF6AAMEGLG4WLEM6ULCTQ%2F&h=36e36daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20170407/F42XWNF6AAMEGLG4WLEM6ULCTQ/</a><br />\n鄭俊弘何雁詩尋日先係朋友 今日就公開拍拖<br />\n<br />\n2018：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/268071/%E4%BB%BB%E5%99%8F%E4%BA%82%E8%A9%95-%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E6%81%86%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E8%BF%AA%E5%AD%90%E6%A1%83%E8%89%B2%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BD%A2%E6%9C%80%E5%81%9A%E9%8C%AF</code></pre><br />\n黃子痕偷食支那女fans<br />\n<br />\n2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=g0R9C-inz2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg0R9C-inz2w&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d3a93d0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=g0R9C-inz2w</a><br />\n<br />\n許志安：我係一個壞左嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200427/2INIQC3QCHRWZ7YAZRR5D42OQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200427%2F2INIQC3QCHRWZ7YAZRR5D42OQQ%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=3d1fb917\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200427%2F2INIQC3QCHRWZ7YAZRR5D42OQQ%2F&h=53532aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200427/2INIQC3QCHRWZ7YAZRR5D42OQQ/</a><br />\n黎振燁車震<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ctwant.com/amp/article/47221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Famp%2Farticle%2F47221&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=51811156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ctwant.com/amp/article/47221</a><br />\n羅志祥多人運動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><ins>呢幾年無論係奀星黎振燁 定係天王巨星羅志祥<br />\n一被爆偷食 <span class=\"gold\">破壞左自己嘅形象</span><br />\n都會出聲交代事件 而且老闆/經理人大多數都會一齊出黎幫手護航<br />\n係咪一到左2021年 呢d事喺fans tg group交代兩句就得<br />\n反正呢d新聞基本上每一年都有<br />\n2022年之後嘅都可以唔交代喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前咁多單嘅藝人都柒左啦<br />\n原來唔洗出黎交代都可以<br />\n小豬、安心真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來唔交代就唔洗比公司雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次保錡連眼藥水都慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9OQi7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9OQi7r.jpg&h=b6900369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfccda2880ddb4efb7f99400373